annotationA: Peroxisomal membrane protein 70 kDa, isoform A; ATPase activity, coupled to transmembrane movement of substances; ATP binding; transporter activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: transmembrane transport; peroxisome organization
annotationB: Gdap1, isoform A; Gdap1 is a transmembrane protein of the outer mitochondrial membrane. Dysregulation of its expression has been related to mitochondrial dynamics, oxidative stress and neuromuscular degeneration
